"title": "5284: cupbearer",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5284: cupbearer",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>One who served a king with wine, often having himself first tasted it for quality and as a safety measure. Some cupbearers became favourites of the king and so wielded considerable political influence.</p>\n<h2>Pharaoh's cupbearer</h2>\n<h3>Imprisoned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:1\">GEN 40:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:5\">GEN 40:5</a></strong></p>\n<h3>His dream</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:9-Gen40:11\">GEN 40:9–40:11</a></p>\n<h3>Dream interpreted by Joseph</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:12-Gen40:14\">GEN 40:12–40:14</a></p>\n<h3>Restored to court</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:21\">GEN 40:21</a></p>\n<h3>Forgetful of Joseph</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:23\">GEN 40:23</a></p>\n<h3>Remembers Joseph</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:9\">GEN 41:9</a></p>\n<h2>Solomon's cupbearers</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:4-1Kgs10:5\">1KI 10:4–10:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:4\">2CH 9:4</a></p>\n<h2>Artaxerxes' cupbearer, Nehemiah</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:11\">NEH 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:1\">NEH 2:1</a></strong></p>",
